# Per Julius's 2026-05-10 rule (tightened, then amended for README):
# all .md and all .txt stay local across every project, EXCEPT
# README.md which is the one approved global exception. Other
# exceptions require explicit per-file approval from Julius.
*.md
*.txt
!README.md
# Internal HTML artefacts (mocks, prototypes, infographics) also stay local.
*-infographic.html
*-mock.html
*-prototype.html
# Public repo-health files (override the broad *.md ignore above)
!SECURITY.md
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
!README.md
!CONTRIBUTORS.md
!.github/**/*.md
